    %p
      Express is a 
      %a{ :href => 'http://nodejs.org' } Node.js
      web development framework created by
      %a{ :href => 'http://twitter.com/tjholowaychuk' } TJ Holowaychuk
      and is loosely based on the 
      %a{ :href => 'http://sinatrarb.com' } Sinatra
      framework for Ruby. Express aims to be one of the fastest and most
      user friendly frameworks on the web, by combining the RESTful Sinatra
      DSL with the raw asynchronous power of node.js.
      
